&lt;p&gt;One of the things I love most about toasters is the occasional frivolity of it all. A toaster that toasts marshmallows&amp;hellip; I mean WHY NOT?!
The Angelus company was also responsible for creating &lt;a href="https://www.campfiremarshmallows.com/campfire-history/"&gt;Cracker Jack&lt;/a&gt;. It seems that they have a knack for delight. This toaster was specifically meant as a &lt;a href="https://americanhistory.si.edu/collections/object/nmah_704103"&gt;promotional tool for their marshmallows&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>